            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="24.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward: Nuria Galceran nuria.galceran@intel.com, and BPM Champion: Rebeca, Meza Redondo &lt;rebeca.meza.redondo@intel.com&gt; of any changes that occur within the flow from now onwards so that changes can be accurately reflected within BIC</text>
